Who has given a cleanchit to China, Modi Govt. We are treated to semantic jugglery. Govt says there are transgressions not incursions.
On each parameter, be it J&K, Naxal, Pak attack, China & North East, there have been increase in attacks against India.
In last 35 months of UPA there were 470 ceasefire violations by Pak & 85 terror incidents. Under Modi Govt, these numbers rose to 1343 & 172
In all these regions we have seen how in most cases the numbers have nearly doubled.: Dr Singhvi
In the North East, between 2011-14 in 229 civilians & 47 jawans lost their lives. After BJP came to power the number rose to 344 & 99.
In Naxal violence, 442 civilians & 278 jawan lost their lives. In the 35 months before Modi Govt took power the numbers were 367 & 268.
In the immediately preceding 35 months, ie 2011-14, 50 civilian & 103 jawans lost their lives. Around half of the current figures.
If you compare the 35 months of this Govt, with the last 35 months of UPA. in J&K 91 civilians & 198 soldiers lost their lives.

My gratitude to all those who are participating in the various programmes. Visiting the vibrant city of Surat is a matter of great joy.
I have been seeing on social media & in the news about a series of events being held across Surat & nearby areas in the run-up to my visit.
Tomorrow in Botad, will also witness the historic welcoming of the waters of the Narmada into the Krishna Sagar Lake.
Will then go to Botad to dedicate to the nation Phase 1 (Link-2) of SAUNI Yojana & lay foundation stone of Phase 2 (Link 2) of SAUNI Yojana.
In Dadra and Nagar Haveli, will inaugurate government projects & distribute sanction letters to beneficiaries of various Govt. initiatives.
Will lay the foundation of various irrigation schemes & inaugurate a drinking water scheme that will benefit people living in Tapi district.
At another programme in Bajipura tomorrow, will inaugurate SUMUL cattle field plant & lay foundation stone for other projects at SUMUL Dairy
Tomorrow in Surat, will inaugurate a multi-speciality hospital at Katargam and a diamond manufacturing unit at Ichhapore.
Later this evening, I will begin my visit to Gujarat as well as Dadra & Nagar Haveli, where I will take part in various programmes tomorrow.

जहां एक तरफ भाजपा शासित राज्य विकास के मापदंड स्थापित कर रहे हैं वहीं ओडिशा में 86% लोग स्वच्छ पीने के पानी से और 41% लोग बिजली से दूर हैं।
